# NixOS Init
1. boot into fresh NixOS installation
2. connect to wifi
3. copy ~/.secret from external drive (just need ssh key really)
4. git clone etc (public source would make this easier & prev step could be removed)
5. activate nix experimental features (TODO rm)
6. run `bash etc/bin/nixos-setup`
7. run `gsettings reset org.gnome.desktop.input-sources xkb-options && gsettings reset org.gnome.desktop.input-sources sources` (TODO: how to automate?)
